responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "0009A43945F281E3656E2080EDF86AEF", "Beware, traveller. Between the goblins trying to breach our defenses and the bandits raiding travellers beyond the walls, it\'s best if you stay near Lionhold. If you\'ve a mind to help, seek Captain Avenmoor in the center of town.")
name: DD_Ambient_Lionhold_Guard_12
